        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group quote-modified\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"169899\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>&lt;\u2026&gt;I intend to do a match tasting \u2026if possible\u2026for vintage 2018 of : Ladoix ( blanc ) by Chevalier vs D-Janthial - Rully ( blanc). I do not know if that would be possible as 2018 Chevalier Ladoix red was released few months ago but not yet for the white.  There is also a possibility it may not come. <img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/2X/8/82916bed5ad74ac8470bc04089d9758b0c80c9fa.gif\" width=\"57\" height=\"28\" alt=\"[drinkers.gif]\" title=\"drinkers\" class=\"animated\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Do keep us posted if you can Peter. I\u2019d love to know the outcome of this comparison.</p>",
