        "created_at": "2021-04-11T18:41:00.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Day 2 on the Rully white: the acidity has slightly subsided giving more place to the fruit. A touch of smoke even appears on the nose. Even better on day 2. Next bottle, I will give it more air and time.</p>",
